

menubar and menu item appear to be on the same level.  they are both
sub classes of the GtkMenuShell object, and both will accept GtkMenuItem
as a child.

GtkMenu is a listing container of GtkMenuItems, (afaik) its only purpose
is to house a list of children.

menubar
    .menuitem
        .menu
            .menuitem
            .menuitem
            .menuitem
            .menuitem


